{"tid":1367331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辛苦哂咁多位香港人","createTime":"2019-07-26T08:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:44:07.000Z","uid":186797,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3def6ee75d723080c2983f94c2df870d50bc3494","tid":1367331,"uid":186797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"呢幾日因為工作問題 去左台灣做野<br />\n岩先機場番黎 見到好多香港人好用心幫手宣傳而家香港情況<br />\n好規矩坐係度表達意見<br />\n岩岩我一落機見到咁情況真係想喊<br />\n岩先係裡面等行李仲聽到有人話我地搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻一個箭步上去大叫香港加油<br />\n出到黎見到好多人派傳單比岩岩出境既旅客<br />\n有位媽媽仲親手比張宣傳單張我<br />\n我話 我都係香港人 我都好支持<br />\n出境果條通道 我都不停重覆叫香港加油 希望可以比大家知道好多外國既香港人都係支持大家<br />\n原諒我要番番屋企換衫放低行李先番到黎幫到手<br />\n大家加油 香港加油 會越黎越多人幫手<br />\n大家千祈唔好氣餒<br />\n<br />\n岩先航班資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLEOZLs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLEOZLs.png&h=38e71496&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba70a21abfa88caf2ec0a02f719410529f69bf7c","tid":1367331,"uid":253880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7520e5cdc36e7d6348f7a3899b9985469d14c0","tid":1367331,"uid":2345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"巴打好野"},{"pid":"af823fc173ac806851aa47669b3e06e63560e080","tid":1367331,"uid":1177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"頭先係咪樓主前面有個大陸西頂住, 然後你衝上前叫香港加油, 好型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b10eba3633658f169d26fc528f7c9302c1a071d","tid":1367331,"uid":186797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba70a21abfa88caf2ec0a02f719410529f69bf7c","tid":1367331,"uid":253880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.